<sect2>
<title>Installation de lesstif</title>

<para>Installez lesstif en lançant les commandes suivantes:</para>

<para><screen><userinput>
./configure --prefix=/usr \
    --enable-build-20 \
    --enable-build-21 \
    --disable-debug \
    --enable-production \
    --disable-build-tests \
    --with-xdnd &amp;&amp;
make &amp;&amp;
make install</userinput></screen></para>

</sect2>

